                        <div id="page-title">
                            三句话外围
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p><strong>前言：</strong>用一小段话（不一定要是三句话）讲述一个故事，每个人都可以参与！</p>
<p>欲查看已归档的原创短篇故事，请<a href="/short-stories-arc">点击这里</a>。</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>创作短篇故事的地方不是用来发布随便想到的段子或无意义玩梗的。</strong>同时请各位投稿人稍微留心一下长度，毕竟八百多字可算不上“三句话”。（为什么不单独投原创呢）</p>
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button create-button" href="/short-stories:00112/parentPage/short-stories/#_editpage">添加新的记录</a></p>
</div>
    
    
    
    </div>
<p style="text-align: center;">显示顺序：<a href="/short-stories/order/name%20desc">最新发布</a> | <a href="/short-stories/created_at/last%207%20day/order/rating%20desc">本周最高</a> | <a href="/short-stories/created_at/last%2030%20day/order/rating%20desc">本月最高</a> | <a href="/short-stories/order/rating%20desc">历史最高</a> | <a href="/short-stories/order/random">随机</a></p>
