<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4055881&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200778" alt="Etinjat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4055881)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;">Etinjat</a></span>：</strong>从归档处转来</p>
